{"tid":198223,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"2017單身人士白表居屋","createTime":"2017-04-12T11:15:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T15:51:25.000Z","uid":66157,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"83bc72a0117fa162d1002aa21313be24f4f797c8","tid":198223,"uid":66157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:15:43.000Z","msg":"單身白表入左表既你９成９都係得梅窩揀<br />\n<br />\n如果有機會買梅窩，係咪真係會去買<br />\n<br />\n會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自己考慮<br />\n1. 居屋福利一世人一次，今次要左，冇下次<br />\n2. 再買樓要俾額外印花稅（睇埋第３點）<br />\n3. 梅窩成交量唔知點，會唔會好難先賣到<br />\n4. 離島加少單位，管理費貴<br />\n5. 出入唔放便，未退休好難長住<br />\n6. 如果唔入去住，買左黎做咩？渡假？<br />\n7. 樓市升係咪會升埋離島居屋？係咪有投資價值<br />\n8. 幾耐先可以補地價放租<br />\n9. 如放租可以有幾多回報<br />\n10. 人工可能加多過入息上限，今次唔要可能冇下次<br />\n<br />\n未知有冇得揀，冇得揀又煩，有得揀又煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人有其他考慮可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef7a48c53f36fd951c0af4faae8c7ef4394c99a4","tid":198223,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:23:51.000Z","msg":"梅窩元朗唔會考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他是但中咩都買"},{"pid":"dfdae1ac0f098331e102654817f5417323f34f1e","tid":198223,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:25:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ebfd46b4578fea2aaab26c93e09150742aea79f","tid":198223,"uid":66157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:26:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>梅窩元朗唔會考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他是但中咩都買</blockquote><br />\n但係單人基本上一定係梅窩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得五十個位，大家都要晒彩虹先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b15b91f46b4ed0ed6015690a3dae47aa3967ad0","tid":198223,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:26:49.000Z","msg":"唔買<br />\n等下次"},{"pid":"38dd844d04ca3b55f36d2df05cb1b4c2fa944916","tid":198223,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:27:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>梅窩元朗唔會考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他是但中咩都買</blockquote><br />\n但係單人基本上一定係梅窩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得總有d西斜，垃圾房付近之類既。同埋如果真係咁搶手點解會有淨餘單位？"},{"pid":"2967a78aff06d467882dc3379dd91b447aa88d08","tid":198223,"uid":85722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:28:03.000Z","msg":"結倫：唔買"},{"pid":"229fb98785e07ff8ec3efb2324b3e23874a00172","tid":198223,"uid":104406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:28:49.000Z","msg":"除非係返中環區 唔係既話唔駛諗<br />\n<br />\n利申 白核"},{"pid":"b7294a78c374c0b223e091ac601bbb761d10aa77","tid":198223,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:30:42.000Z","msg":"同老人家一齊抽會唔會易d?<br />\n想抽彩虹嗰個"},{"pid":"e8d480771cb2d0a1a360817c681b107d2641eca6","tid":198223,"uid":66157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:30:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>梅窩元朗唔會考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他是但中咩都買</blockquote><br />\n但係單人基本上一定係梅窩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得總有d西斜，垃圾房付近之類既。同埋如果真係咁搶手點解會有淨餘單位？</blockquote><br />\n有啲好似係揀完但唔要冇成交放返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f72ad21197a92fec76909b134cbe813786faef06","tid":198223,"uid":104406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime